      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a daily driver that still delivers exhilarating performance. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with standard highway use. Inside, the black leather interior is in great shape; it has been kept strictly smoke-free and the rear seats appear nearly untouched, while the driver\u2019s seat shows only light, natural creasing on the bolster. Mechanically, this Macan is robust, featuring a complete service history with the most recent maintenance performed just 500 miles ago. All cabin electronics, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and Bose premium sound system, function perfectly. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, turn-key luxury SUV that has been cared for and is ready for its next chapter.",
